---
title: Beef & Black Bean Taquitos with Charred Corn Salsa & Enchilada Sauce
description: Taquitos, enchiladas, quesadillas ... whatever you like to call them, these black bean-filled tortillas are a household name.
By switching beef to beans, you can still get all of your favourite Mexican flavours in this delicious meal! Dig in!
